high_descs: Turn around and face the end of the long table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Walk around the table to face the tomato on the table.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and step forward to face the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the trash can.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat a slice of tomato and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around to go to the right side of gray table against the wall.
Pick up the gray knife on the table.
Go to the front of the table.
Slice only half of the red bell pepper.
Turn around and go to the microwave above the sink.
Place the gray knife in the microwave.
Turn around to go back to the white table.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Turn around to go back to the microwave.
Microwave the slice of tomato next to the gray knife and take it out.
Turn right to go to the brass trash can on the floor.
Place the slice of tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Microwave the slice of tomato and throw it away.

high_descs: Walk backwards, turn to the left and walk to the table that the coffee pot is on.
Pick up the solid silver knife from the table.
Turn to the left and walk around the table the the opposite side.
Slice the tomato that is on the front, left corner beside the salt shaker.
Turn to the right and walk over to the sink with knife in hand.
Open the microwave door that is above the sink, place the knife inside and close the door.
Turn to the right and walk back to the table.
Pick up a tomato slice.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Open the microwave door above the sink, place the tomato slice inside, close the door, open the door, remove the tomato, close the door.
Turn right and walk to the trash bin.
Toss the tomato slice into the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw a warm tomato slice into the trash.
